    <summary>Describes a service for reporting text line information in XAML reader implementations.</summary>
    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 <xref:System.Xaml.XamlXmlReader> implements <xref:System.Xaml.IXamlLineInfo>. <xref:System.Xaml.XamlXmlReader> returns <xref:System.Xaml.IXamlLineInfo> values that are based on the position of the XAML reader at the time of the call.  
  
 Line number information might be reported in exceptions such as <xref:System.Xaml.XamlParseException>.  
  
 ]]></format>
    </remarks>
